#CircuitBreakerSG D-42

Chasing away my Monday Blues with Rainbow Quinoa Salad
🥗 Rinse & cook Quinoa (1 part quinoa to 2 parts water or stock).
🥗 Cut Tomato, Avocado, Golden Kiwi & Mandarin Orange.
🥗 Prepare homemade vinaigrette of Extra Virgin Olive Oil, Lemon Juice, Apple Cider Vinegar, Honey, Salt & Garlic Pepper.
🥗 Drizzle Vinaigrette over cut ingredients & Quinoa.
🥗 Toss well & serve with homemade Granola.

#NoMondayBlues
